    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-03-07T08:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-03-07T08:00:00-05:00" n="561"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d561">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/4600: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Switzerland (<persName corresp="#p_WHR1"
                            type="from">Wilson</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-03-07T14:00:00+01:00"
                            >March 7, 1932—2 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received March 7—9 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>58. Have had conversations this morning with both <persName corresp="#p_YWW1"
                        >Yen</persName> and <persName corresp="#p_ORE1">Olds</persName>. Their ideas
                    run along the same line as yours as to the conversations which can be
                    immediately undertaken.</p>
                <p>As our thoughts run along similar general lines we will be asked in conversations
                    with representatives of other states to push for same objective.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_WHR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
